<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08101</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT GRANTING SURVIVORSHIP BENEFITS TO THE DEPENDENT CHILDREN OF A DECEASED RETIRED MEMBER OF THE JUDICIARY WHO IS A SOLO PARENT, OR TO THE SURVIVING PARENTS OR NOMINATED PERSONS OF SUCH DECEASED RETIREE, AMENDING FOR THE PURPOSE REPUBLIC ACT NO. 910, AS AMENDED, AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE :  Granting Survivorship Benefits To The Dependent Children Of A Deceased Retired Member Of The Judiciary Who Is A Solo Parent, Or To The Surviving Parents Or Nominated Persons Of Such Deceased Retiree</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides for retirement benefits to the dependent children when the unmarried justice or judge is a solo parent or have dependent under his care; or to the surviving parents, if any, or any person or persons, unless disqualified by law, nominated by the judge or justice who died without issue.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>FARI&Ntilde;AS, RODOLFO C., UMALI, REYNALDO V., NOGRALES, KARLO ALEXEI B., VELOSO, VICENTE &quot;CHING&quot; S.E., DE VERA, EUGENE MICHAEL B., CUEVA, LEO RAFAEL M., HERRERA-DY, BERNADETTE &quot;BH&quot; C., SY-ALVARADO, JOSE ANTONIO &quot;KUYA JONATHAN&quot; R., BELMONTE, RICARDO &quot;RJ&quot; JR. T., TAMBUNTING, GUS S., ZAMORA, MARIA CARMEN S., LEACHON, DOY C., DEL MAR, RAUL V., LOBREGAT, CELSO L., NU&Ntilde;EZ-MALANYAON, CORAZON T., VILLAFUERTE, LUIS RAYMUND JR. F., ANTONINO, MAGNOLIA C., SAMBAR, MARK AERON H., CAMINERO, WILFREDO S.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-08-14</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Uybarreta (000 2018-11-15)</td><td>2. Salo (000 2018-11-15)</td><tr><td>3. Alonte (000 2018-11-15)</td><td>4. Garcia (J.E.) (000 2018-11-15)</td><tr><td colspan=3>AUTHORS(Final/Third Readi